WEBVTT

00:02:59.647 --> 00:03:04.036
and good sleep practices can help rebuild 
your relationship with bedtime.

00:03:04.036 --> 00:03:07.550
Make sure your bedroom is dark 
and comfortably cool

00:03:07.550 --> 00:03:10.486
to minimize “threats” during hyperarousal.

00:03:10.486 --> 00:03:12.515
Only use your bed for sleeping,

00:03:12.515 --> 00:03:13.720
and if you’re restless,

00:03:13.720 --> 00:03:17.855
leave the room and tire yourself out 
with relaxing activities

00:03:17.855 --> 00:03:18.773
like reading,

00:03:18.773 --> 00:03:19.608
meditating,

00:03:19.608 --> 00:03:20.894
or journaling.

00:03:20.894 --> 00:03:25.737
Regulate your metabolism by setting
consistent resting and waking times

00:03:25.737 --> 00:03:29.018
to help orient 
your body’s biological clock.

